name: Shaolin's Aura
description:
In a temple, above the clouds there is Shaolin Kung Fu ready to fight with inner strength that reflects the aura of each warrior from various dojos, they fight in their own style, Warrior with spear and scroll holds orange aura, Swordsmen holds green aura , The Old Master with his bare hands holds blue aura, and the Female Fighters with her kicks holds white aura.

To celebrate 500 followers.

Thanks!
